      "writtenOn": "2020-12-08T20:42:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good point, I actually didn\u0027t thought about externally reported case. I imagine this is purely set by CV because ideally, it is CV who cancels those no-longer-needed tryjobs. But nothing prevents user from going to the build UI and cancelling the Tryjob themselves.\n\nWhat is the current CQ behavior in this scenario? Does CQ consider it as a failure and retry?",
